document_data.mainbody: '''Palace Street''' was a road located in the city of [[Skuld]] in [[Mulhorand]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite interactive atlas|490 Skuld}}
document_data.Location: Palace Street was found in the central section of Skuld in the [[Skuld/Central Ward|Central Ward]]. The street originated at the entrance to the [[Skuld/Palace District|Palace District]] where it ran southeast through the Central Ward before ending near the [[East Gate (Skuld)|East Gate]].
